{"tid":1595601,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[廣傳+舉報] 疑假冒義務律師FB Page 唔知係咪想偷義士資料！","createTime":"2019-09-26T06:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T02:00:39.000Z","uid":193592,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"6e6d0e61c10889bc7f8736daf2dda4ab33671c1e","tid":1595601,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:40:57.000Z","msg":"話說FB上面有個咁既page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">「大律師及律師事務所-香港 Barristers and Solicitors Law Firm Hong Kong」<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6zTxMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6zTxMC.png&h=3842bbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前幾日偷/借左篇文出左個post<br />\n講到自己係義務律師咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lawfirmshk/photos/a.2402246339854054/2591693737575979/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flawfirmshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.2402246339854054%2F2591693737575979%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=57b28643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lawfirmshk/photos/a.2402246339854054/2591693737575979/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n（又比佢呃到幾千like）<br />\n<br />\n呢篇文係反送中義務律師 陳信忻寫既<br />\n（雖然係個post最底都有貼link）<br />\n但條友係個post口口聲聲話「以下的內容和我們這3個月親眼見的差別不大」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過冇人識得page主啵</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ia5zhgx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fia5zhgx.png&h=cc4da6db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">FC左既係：<br />\n民權監察的律師冇一個人識佢<br />\n事務律師/ 大律師執業名單冇佢</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你唔係執業律師<br />\n請問你點做到義務律師？點去「親眼見」到被捕人士乜乜乜？<br />\n喂，你菲律賓大學的證書都冇張<br />\n（FB:「在 HKU SPACE Law 讀刑事法、民事法、公司法、侵權法、基本法、國際法」）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">咁既然唔係律師<br />\n都冇咩專業操守要守既<br />\n咁開個咁既page想收集義士資料<br />\n有咩居心先？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以提提大家<br />\n有事都係搵番星火/民陣/民權啦<br />\n請必廣傳+舉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de29891eadd374eca65e33888cd9352db6c7161c","tid":1595601,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:41:27.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"01d547df16064a6f25916b0be7ac38da6b3e3430","tid":1595601,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a4bb735379ef66f8b27e43165f93646e675818cd","tid":1595601,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"2875776ffda20bc405e5953f54f96e131c90590a